data.description: Beautiful home conveniently located in town. 4 bedroom 2 bath with a fenced yard. This home features hardwood flooring and a split floor plan. Master suite has a walk in closet, Jetted tub with a separate shower. Updated window's and  a 50 year roof. Solar panels for lower electrical bills. Must see this home. Owner to give a 1 year home warranty valued at 500.00. Owner willing to use Assumption
